OL,3,C'We've got a powerful voice now':
OL,4,CSummerland campaigners announce legal
OL,5,Cbacking
OL,7,FA campaign to overturn the inquest
OL,8,Fverdicts of those who died in the
OL,9,FSummerland disaster has taken a step
OL,10,Fforward after a leading solicitor said
OL,11,Fthe Government "must take action".
OL,13,FThe Justice For Summerland Campaign
OL,14,FGroup says it will now formally apply
OL,15,Fto the island's Attorney General for a
OL,16,Ffresh inquest into .
OL,18,FThe fire at the Summerland holiday
OL,19,Fcomplex in 1973 killed 50 people,
OL,20,Famong them were eleven children.
