OL,4,CSummerland campaigners announce legal
OL,5,Cbacking
OL,7,FIn the years that have passed, the
OL,8,Fcampaign say nobody has ever been held
OL,9,Faccountable.
OL,11,FHowever, the group now has the backing
OL,12,Fof Darragh Mackin, one of the
OL,13,Fsolicitors involved in overturning the
OL,14,Finquest verdict in the landmark Case
OL,15,Fin Dublin in May.
