OL,3,C'We've got a powerful voice now':
OL,4,CSummerland campaigners announce legal
OL,5,Cbacking
OL,7,FMr Mackin has already written to the
OL,8,Fisland's Attorney General informing
OL,9,Fhim of the Summerland campaign's
OL,10,Fintentions, and the hope to overturn
OL,11,Fthe 'death by misadventure' verdict
OL,12,Fplaced on all 50 victims of the
OL,13,Ftragedy.
OL,15,FThe Northern Irish solicitor, who
OL,16,Fworks for Phoenix Law, described the
OL,17,Finquest findings as "exceptionally
OL,18,Fconcerning".
