OL,3,C'We've got a powerful voice now':
OL,4,CSummerland campaigners announce legal
OL,5,Cbacking
OL,7,FHe said: "In an almost identical set
OL,8,Fof circumstances with the Stardust
OL,9,Ffire, a fresh inquest, we say, can,
OL,10,Fthrough the right mechanism, call
OL,11,Fwitnesses, hear expert evidence, and
OL,12,Festablish the truth.
OL,14,F"My initial reaction when I understood
OL,15,Fthe original verdict of misadventure
OL,16,Fwas one of utmost concern," Mr Mackin
OL,17,Fsaid.
