OL,7,F"When you look closer and you look
OL,8,Funder the bonnet as to how that
OL,9,Fverdict was achieved, it's
OL,10,Fexceptionally concerning."
OL,12,FMr Mackin is taking on the Summerland
OL,13,Fcase after .
OL,15,FIn 1981, a fire ripped through a
OL,16,Fnightclub in Artane, north Dublin in
OL,17,Fthe largest ever disaster in the
OL,18,Fhistory of the Irish state.
