OL,3,C'We've got a powerful voice now':
OL,4,CSummerland campaigners announce legal
OL,5,Cbacking
OL,7,FAn initial inquiry into the Stardust
OL,8,Ftragedy found that 'arson' was the
OL,9,Flikely cause of the fire, but this was
OL,10,Flater quashed, kickstarting a campaign
OL,11,Ffor justice as fresh inquests were
OL,12,Fordered.
OL,14,FThis led to a new inquest opening on
OL,15,F25 April 2023, where a jury heard how
OL,16,Fmany fire exits were locked, chained
OL,17,For obstructed - mirroring various
OL,18,Feyewitness accounts at Summerland.
