OL,3,C'We've got a powerful voice now':
OL,4,CSummerland campaigners announce legal
OL,5,Cbacking
OL,7,FThe campaign, backed by Mr Mackin,
OL,8,Fended with conclusive verdicts of
OL,9,F'unlawful killing' - successfully
OL,10,Foverturning the original inquest
OL,11,Fverdict after 40 years.
OL,13,FHeather Lea lost both her parents,
OL,14,FRichard and Elizabeth Cheetham, and
OL,15,Fher 13-year-old sister June in the
OL,16,FSummerland fire.
OL,18,FShe said having the services of a
OL,19,Flawyer with Mr Mackin's stature and
OL,20,Fexperience had given the campaign a
OL,21,Fhuge boost.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/14
