OL,3,C'We've got a powerful voice now':
OL,4,CSummerland campaigners announce legal
OL,5,Cbacking
OL,7,F"It's an amazing feat for us to get
OL,8,Fhim, it's brilliant," she said, adding
OL,9,Fthat the constitutional arrangements
OL,10,Fof the Isle of Man mean they may have
OL,11,Fan uphill battle to convince the
OL,12,Fgovernment in Douglas to reopen the
OL,13,FSummerland case.
OL,15,F"They've brushed it under the carpet
OL,16,Ffor 50 years, and with Darragh being
OL,17,Finvolved I'm hoping now they'll stand
OL,18,Fup, listen and say 'this is an
OL,19,Finjustice, and we've got to put it
OL,20,Fright," she said.
