OL,3,C'We've got a powerful voice now':
OL,4,CSummerland campaigners announce legal
OL,5,Cbacking
OL,7,FHeather's husband Reg added: "We've
OL,8,Fgot a powerful voice now, it's not
OL,9,Fjust individual people or groups of
OL,10,Fpeople, it's somebody who is a
OL,11,Fprominent international lawyer who can
OL,12,Fmake things happen.
OL,14,F"How long it will take I don't know,
OL,15,Fbut I'm more optimistic than I was
OL,16,Fbefore.
OL,18,F"I think we might get the verdict
OL,19,Foverturned, but we've got a long way
OL,20,Fto go yet".
