OL,12,F"The Attorney General can confirm a
OL,13,Fletter was received yesterday from Mr
OL,14,FMackin.
OL,16,F"Consideration is currently being
OL,17,Fgiven to its contents and a response
OL,18,Fwill be delivered in due course."
