OL,3,C'We've got a powerful voice now':
OL,4,CSummerland campaigners announce legal
OL,5,Cbacking
OL,7,FIt comes after the Chief Minister
OL,8,Fapologised for the 'pain, harm and
OL,9,Ffailings' of the disaster, during a
OL,10,Fsitting of Tynwald in July 2023.
OL,12,FThis was followed by a national
OL,13,Fservice of remembrance for the 50th
OL,14,Fanniversary in August.
OL,16,FWhile Mr Mackin recognised the Chief
OL,17,FMinister had 'acknowledged the
OL,18,Fwrongdoing', he said 'it doesn't go
OL,19,Fanywhere near to resolving the
OL,20,Fproblem'.
