OL,3,C'We've got a powerful voice now':
OL,4,CSummerland campaigners announce legal
OL,5,Cbacking
OL,7,FComparing Stardust with Summerland, Mr
OL,8,FMackin said: "The reality is both have
OL,9,Fbeen riddled with failed
OL,10,Finvestigations, in my view.
OL,12,F"And secondly, both have at the
OL,13,Fepicentre a previous finding that
OL,14,Findeed almost puts blame on the very
OL,15,Fvictims who went there.
OL,17,F"The verdict in this Summerland of
OL,18,F'misadventure' attaches with the
OL,19,Fabsence of any blame or
OL,20,Fresponsibility, and the absence of any
OL,21,Fculpability for any other person.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/14
