OL,3,C'We've got a powerful voice now':
OL,4,CSummerland campaigners announce legal
OL,5,Cbacking
OL,7,F"That, many of the families believe,
OL,8,Fis an insult to them and an insult to
OL,9,Ftheir loved ones.
OL,11,F"It's for those reasons that they're
OL,12,Falmost identical in that both sides of
OL,13,Ffamilies have, in essence, been
OL,14,Fcampaigning for four decades for an
OL,15,Feffective investigation in both
OL,16,Fscenarios.
OL,18,F"And like we've seen with the
OL,19,FStardust, even despite the passage of
OL,20,Ftime with an effective investigation,
OL,21,Fthe truth can be established."
